<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>PRAYZVIBES | Faith. Sound. Vibes.</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111 0%, #000 100%);
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
}

.container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 60px 20px;
}

.logo img {
    width: 150px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 3px solid #d4af37;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}

h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.description {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    opacity: 0.85;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.button {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 400px;
    margin: 15px auto;
    padding: 15px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 10px;
    transition: 0.3s ease;
}

.primary {
    background: #d4af37;
    color: #000;
}

.primary:hover {
    background: #fff;
}

.secondary {
    border: 2px solid #d4af37;
    color: #d4af37;
}

.secondary:hover {
    background: #d4af37;
    color: #000;
}

footer {
    margin-top: 60px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    opacity: 0.6;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

    <!-- Replace logo.png with your uploaded logo file -->
    <div class="logo">
        <img src="logo.png" alt="PRAYZVIBES Logo">
    </div>

    <h1>PRAYZVIBES</h1>

    <div class="description">
        PRAYZVIBES blends faith and music into one powerful experience.<br><br>
        Prayer in the heart. Praise in the sound. Positive energy in every vibe.
    </div>

    <a href="#" class="button primary">🎵 Listen Now</a>
    <a href="#" class="button secondary">🙏 Join the Movement</a>
    <a href="https://instagram.com/prayzvibes" class="button secondary">📸 Instagram</a>
    <a href="#" class="button secondary">🎥 TikTok</a>

    <footer>
        © 2026 PRAYZVIBES. All Rights Reserved.
    </footer>

</div>

</body>
</html>
